Event Title: SURFER BLOOD • Winter - Tickets - Club Dada - Dallas, TX - February 3rd, 2021
Event Description: SURFER BLOOD's rescheduled show from Not So Fun Wknd 2020. Bringing WINTER with them at it is in winter. It will probably be so cold out. Surfer Blood have just finished recording their 5th album, which will be coming out on July 17, 2020, alongside a 10th anniversary reissue of their debut album Astro Coast. Surfer Blood's music is renowned for catchy hooks and sonic detail. One of the best indie guitar bands around, founding members John Paul Pitts and Tyler Schwarz are joined by guitarist Michael McCleary and bassist Lindsey Mills, all four alumni of the same high school in West Palm Beach, Florida.Surfer Blood are the cleanest and nicest band in existence.
